' @test valid
' @covers RESULT, CHOICE
' @description RESULT with CHOICE enum field

THINK triage
  GOAL <<
  Determine the severity of the issue.
  >>
  RESULT
  * severity: CHOICE(critical, high, medium, low) - issue severity
  * category: CHOICE(bug, feature, question) - issue type
END

WAIT
  ON ?triage
END

EXIT
